{{Quote|This from the guy who once kicked a hole in a wall when he lost a patient to Drakñahr Syndrome&mdash;something that all of Coruscant Med and a room full of Jedi and Silents couldn't treat.|[[Zan Yant]], to [[Jos Vondar]]|<ref name="MedStar I">''[[MedStar I: Battle Surgeons]]''</ref>}}
'''Drakñahr Syndrome''' was an obscure disease that struck without warning, often confusing doctors who were treating it as another illness. It was notable for being incredibly resistant to treatment of any kind; the entirety of [[Coruscant Medical]] and a roomful of [[Jedi healer/Legends|Jedi healers]] and [[The Silent|Silent]] were unable to cure one of [[Jos Vondar]]'s patients afflicted with the syndrome.

